title: Cherub Complete Discography + Bonus (Oct 2014)
description:
Everything is in as close to authentic 320 as I could find. Entire discography including two tracks off 'Year of the Caprese' only available in Japan and off of the Vinyl. Enjoy and seed please! I will try my best to seed as this is my first torrent, any and all feedback is appreciated.
